query:
SELECT numeroCi, tipoServicoCompra, valorTotal, mesServico, YEAR(createdAt) as ano 
FROM despesas_v2 
WHERE mesServico = 'dezembro' 
  AND YEAR(createdAt) = 2025
  AND tipoServicoCompra LIKE '%Equipamentos%'
